    {
      "title": "WARGEAR ABILITIES",
      "entries": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Remote Mine: Once per battle, at the start of your Shooting phase , you can select one enemy unit within 9\" of and visible to the bearer and roll one D6: on a 3+, that enemy unit suffers D3 mortal wounds , or 2D3 mortal wounds instead if it is a VEHICLE or FORTIFICATIONS unit. Designer\u2019s Note: Place a Remote Mine token next to the unit, removing it once this ability has been used."
        }
